sql_statement.static: SELECT Iteration, "Router Count", "Route Rx Count", "Convergence Time (s)", "Configured Timeout (s)" FROM BgpRRClientConvergence

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT MIN("Convergence Time (s)" <= "Configured Timeout (s)") FROM BgpRRClientConvergence

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: Client convergence time was within the configured timeout value.
report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: The test timed out. Client convergence time was greater than the configured timeout value.
